purpose: Schedule a meeting to discuss the new AI-powered OCR system for bill processing. Find out what time works this week.

messages.content: Hi! Sorry, let me clarify - I'm calling on behalf of Naveen Valsakumar to schedule a meeting with you this week about the new AI-powered OCR system for bill processing. What day works best for you?
Wait, wait, can you repeat that?
Of course! Naveen would like to meet with you this week to discuss an AI-powered OCR system for processing bills. What day and time works for your schedule?
Can you repeat what you calling about?

Absolutely! We're calling to set up a meeting about a new OCR system - that's technology that reads and processes bills automatically using AI. Naveen wants to discuss this with you. Does any day this week work for a meeting?
Perfect! I'll schedule Naveen to meet with you today at 3:00 p.m. to discuss the OCR system. Thanks so much for your time!
You're welcome! Have a great day!
